🦁 Riget Zoo Adventure (RZA) – Desktop Application

Riget Zoo Adventure (RZA) is a full-featured desktop application designed to simulate a real-world zoo management and visitor booking system. The application combines GUI development with backend database management to provide a seamless and interactive user experience.

📌 Project Overview

The application allows users to:

Register and log in securely

Purchase zoo tickets

Book hotel rooms

Explore membership plans (Silver & Gold)

Earn and manage reward points

View zoo information, map, prices, and opening times

Access educational visit information

Browse food and drink services

The system integrates frontend interface design with a SQLite database backend.

🎯 Key Features
👤 User Account Management

User Registration with validation

Secure Login Authentication

Membership selection

User profile management

Points accumulation system

🎟 Ticket Booking System

Select date and time slot

Choose ticket type:

Standard Adult

Standard Child

Standard Student

Saver Ticket (2 adults + 2 children)

Add to basket functionality

🏨 Hotel Booking System

Select check-in and check-out dates

